& [CurrentAttentionRuntimeRegistryState] is the live semantic registry for active attention
  + [registry_status] is active
  + [registry_scope] is validated LM Studio launch result over task-frame launch queue
  + [active_root_frame] is attention_frame_2026_06_24_lmstudio_launch_result_001
  + [active_frame_count] is 1
  + [suspended_frame_count] is 0
  + [closed_frame_count] is 0
  + [return_anchor] is C:\Project\Pinky\.sop\state\CurrentFocalPoint.sop
  + [registry_outside] is hidden activations, exact transformer attention, model weights, worker mutation authority, broad task competence, and unrelated Pinky worktree changes

  = must: update this state when focus materially changes
  = must: preserve return anchors before closing or suspending frames
  = must: keep the registry semantic and visible, not native-runtime or hidden-state based
  = should: stay compact enough for context-compression re-entry

& [AttentionFrame_2026_06_24_LMStudioLaunchResult001] is the active semantic stack frame for the validated LM Studio launch result
  + [frame_id] is attention_frame_2026_06_24_lmstudio_launch_result_001
  + [frame_state] is active
  + [parent_frame] is none
  + [child_frame_set] is functional_lmstudio_lane, one_minute_heartbeat, operating_loop_tick_003, task_frame_launch_result, lmstudio_next_probe_001, commit_receipt
  + [return_anchor] is C:\Project\Pinky\.sop\state\CurrentFocalPoint.sop
  + [frame_trace] is TaskFrameLaunchQueue.sop, 2026-06-24_lmstudio_next_probe_result_001.sop, sop_inference_comparison_lmstudio_next_probe_20260624_008.sop, 2026-06-24_operating_loop_tick_003.sop, LMStudioWorkerFunctionalLane.sop, and CurrentFocalPoint.sop
  + [focus_register] is validated score 100 LM Studio proposal from scratch-isolated task-frame launch
  + [question_register] is whether to integrate validated LM Studio proposal evidence into LMStudioWorkerFunctionalLane readiness profile
  + [delineation_register] is inside launch_result, result_file, validation_score, validation_band, integration_disposition, and result_outside
  + [periphery_register] is model metadata warnings, no project-root authority, proposal-not-integrated boundary, validator gate, and unrelated dirty files outside
  + [operation_register] is inspect_queue_candidate, run_scratch_isolated_launch, validate_output, capture_result, emit_tick_003, update_reentry_state
  + [evidence_register] is result_001, captured worker output 008, validation score 100, and operating_loop_tick_003
  + [wisdom_register] is repeated isolated score 100 strengthens lane evidence without becoming broad competence proof
  + [caution_register] is validated proposal does not self-integrate and stderr warnings remain outside
  + [balance_register] is stable because launch was isolated, output captured, validation passed, and outside preserved
  + [integration_register] is pending commit, push, and Codex review for readiness-profile integration
  + [frame_outside] is hidden model state, broad local-worker readiness, worker file mutation, remote claims before push, and unrelated workspace changes

  = must: treat this frame as current visible attention state
  = must: return clock_state, proof_state, balance_state, drive_state, next_step, and outside to CurrentFocalPoint when this focus pass closes
  = should: open child frames only when a concrete benchmark, scoring, or worker-profile pass is needed

(current_attention_runtime_registry_state) :active_root_frame: /semantic_register_set and return_anchor/ |registry_outside|
  + [active_root_frame] is attention_frame_2026_06_24_lmstudio_launch_result_001
  + [semantic_register_set] is focus, question, delineation, periphery, operation, evidence, Wisdom, Caution, balance, and integration registers
  + [return_anchor] is CurrentFocalPoint
  |registry_outside| hidden model state, executable runtime stack, unreviewed worker authority, unrelated dirty files, and untracked cognition

/ [CurrentFocalPoint], [AttentionRuntimeRegistry], [TaskFrameLaunchQueue] -(EntersFrame)> [AttentionFrame_2026_06_24_LMStudioLaunchResult001], [registry_outside]
* [semantic_register_set], [return_anchor], [frame_trace] -(SupportsReentry)> [launch_result], [operating_loop_tick], [balance_register], [integration_register], [outside]
